content.rendered:
Directed by Sandeep Reddy Vanga.

Written by Wajid Shaikh. Siddharth-Garima. Siddharth Singh. Sandeep Reddy Vanga. Garima Wahal.

Cast Shahid Kapoor(Kabir Rajdheer Singh). Kiara Advani(Preeti Sikka). Nikita Dutta(Jia Sharma). Soham Majumdar(Shiva). Arjan Bajwa(Karan Rajdheer Singh). Suresh Oberoi(Rajdheer Singh). Kamini Kaushal(Sadhna Kaur- Kabir’s daadi). Adil Hussain(Dean Himanshu Joshi). Amit Sharma(Amit). Anurag Arora(Harpal Sikka). Dolly Minhas(Kabir’s Mother). Aanchal Chauhan(Karan’s Wife). Suparna Marwah(Preeti’s Mother). Swati Seth(Vidya). Anusha Sampath(Keerti). Parakh Madan(Preeti’s sister). Gagandeep Singh(Jatinder- Preeti’s husband). Maneka Kurup Arora(Judge). Urvashi Panchal(Nurse Durga). Siya Mahajan(Nurse Raani). Vipul Deshpande(Hospital Director). Priyaa Rauniyar(Shiva’s sister (as Priya Roniyar)) . Rajat Arora(Fractured Patient). Backagaindancer(Kabira). Ankush Deshmukh(Laxman). Ragini Dev(College Girl).Pooja Dey. Aditya Jawalkar(Preeti’s Society Friend). Danish Kalra(Future Brother-in-law). Mahi Kamla(Brothel Girl). Ashim Kemson(Beggar – Guy who sang ‘Fakir Jatt da’). Mohammad Salman Khan(Salman). Vanita Kharat(Kabir’s Maid). Pankaj Kumar(Coordinator). 

Language Hindi.

Producers Naman Chouhan. Jatin Pawan Girotra. Naina Jhanjee. Himanshu Joshi. Murad Khetani. Niraj Kothari. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Yogiraj Shetty. Navmeet Singh. Harshveer Srivastava. Mayank Tiwari. Ashwin Varde.

Production Cine1 Studios. T-Series.
